            <h3><a href="#"  data-metrics='{"action":"Toggle Footer Dropdown","label":"About","category":"All Tech Considered"}' >About</a></h3>
      <div id="footer_module" class="agglocation linkLocation">
                  <div id="res163884901" class="bucketwrap listtext">
                        <div class="bucket">
                              <p>All Tech Considered explores how technology is changing culture and connection. It's hosted by <a href="http://www.npr.org/people/144449221/elise-hu" target="_blank">Elise Hu</a>, with contributions from technology correspondents <a href="http://www.twitter.com/hennseggs">Steve Henn</a>, <a href="http://www.npr.org/people/2101272/laura-sydell">Laura Sydell</a> and other curious NPR journalists. Reach us on Twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/npralltech">@NPRAllTech</a> or <a href="http://help.npr.org/npr/includes/customer/npr/custforms/contactus.aspx?sid=80">contact us via our handy form</a>. </p>
